    section.summary
      h3 Hey, I'm Ernest.
      .hairline.columns.small-2.large-1.small-centered
      .columns.small-12.medium-8.large-8.small-centered
        p.summary-text
          | I'm currently studying Computer Engineering at the <a href="http://uwaterloo.ca">University of Waterloo</a> and I like to code in my spare time. Recently, I've worked at <a href="http://boltmade.com">Boltmade</a> as a co-op doing full-stack web dev. I've also done a bunch of <a href="#projects">Android projects</a> for fun, and I'm always eager to learn new things. You can check out my stuff on <a href="http://github.com/ernestwong">Github</a>, have a look at <a href="ernest-resume.pdf">my resume</a>, give me a <a href="mailto:ewong2222@hotmail.com">shout</a>, or just take a look around.
    section#projects
      h1 Projects
      .hairline.columns.small-2.large-1.small-centered
      .projects-container.row
        .columns.large-8.medium-10.large-8.medium-centered
          .project-item
            h3 Sudoku Solver
            a(href="http://github.com/ernestwong/sudokusolver")
              .project-img-container
                img(src="css/img/project/sudoku-before-nophone.png")
                img(src="css/img/project/sudoku-after-nophone.png")
            p Simply take a picture of a Sudoku puzzle and have the solution in front of you. Uses OpenCV to process image and Tesseract OCR to detect digits. Implemented backtracking algorithm to solve sudoku puzzle.
            a(href="http://github.com/ernestwong/sudokusolver") Github
          .project-item
            h3 Connectd
            a(href="https://connectd.herokuapp.com")
              .project-img-container
                img(src="css/img/project/connectd-screen-1.png")
            p Get Connectd with anyone with a single click. Ruby on Rails application that allows user to send invitations simultaneously via all social media platforms to another user.
            p 
              | <a href="http://github.com/ernestwong/connectd">Github</a> | <a href="https://connectd.herokuapp.com/">Website</a>
          .project-item
            h3 UWInfoSession
            a(href="http://github.com/ernestwong/uwinfosession")
              .project-img-container
                img(src="css/img/project/uwinfo-1-nophone.png")
                img(src="css/img/project/uwinfo-2-nophone.png")
            p A simple Android application that retrieves data from Waterloo API and displays upcoming information sessions. Can view individual event details and add event to system calendar.
            a(href="http://github.com/ernestwong/uwinfosession") Github
          .project-item
            h3 MuseDreams
            a(href="http://github.com/ernestwong/musedreams")
              .project-img-container
                img(src="css/img/project/musedreams-code.png")
                img(src="css/img/project/muse-headband.png")
            p Have a worry-free nap with MuseDreams. An IoT (Internet of Things) hack created at WesternHacks with the Muse headband that makes adjustments to external surroundings when user is falling asleep. Interprets input data from headband via state machine and uploads user alertness status to server where Android phone and Arduino responds.
            p 
              | <a href="http://github.com/ernestwong/musedreams">Github</a> | <a href="http://hackwestern.challengepost.com/submissions/34909-musedreams?utm_campaign=hack-western-2015_20141210&utm_content=submission_visible_in_gallery&utm_medium=email&utm_source=transactional">ChallengePost</a>
